text: Deena Nicole Buckner (born Deena Nicole Cortese; January 12, 1987) is an American reality television personality. She appeared on the MTV reality show Jersey Shore from 2010 to 2012. In November 2016, Cortese became engaged to Christopher Buckner. They were married on October 28, 2017. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Television personalities from New Jersey
